The VEDA API source code is currently stored in a private repository: delta-backend but is based off eoAPI





STAC API (metadata): https://dev-stac.delta-backend.xyz/docs Raster API (tiling): https://dev-raster.delta-backend.xyz/docs STAC viewer: https://dev-stac.delta-backend.xyz/index.html





STAC API (metadata): https://staging-stac.delta-backend.xyz/docs

In this notebook you will find documentation for the various APIs for the datasets maintained by NASA VEDA project.
In addition you will find example notebooks on how to use those APIs and datasets.
